## Package
Package for getting weather data using a zipcode.

## Usage
```python
from the_weather import *

weather = Weather(22025)

d = weather.daily_forecast("2023-09-17")
print(d[0])

# Output
Sunday 2023-09-17 [05:00 PM] - 19Â° 50%: Scattered Showers

```
